X_t = \sum_{i=0}^N \frac{T_{N+1-i}}{2^i} 
E[X_t|N] = \sum_{i=0}^N \frac{E[T_{N+1-i}|N]}{2^i}  = \frac{t}{N+1}\left(2 - \frac{1}{2^N}\right).
